 into two departments in  institutional banking  markets ibm and business  private banking bpb ibm includes areas of the bank that provides services to institutional clients and global markets bpb includes areas of the bank that provides services to business customers and private banking customers wealth managementedit wealth management brings together the groups funds management platform master funds superannuation insurance and financial advice business support colonial first state colonial first state global asset management and comminsure all form part of wealth management cba has been granted a mysuper authority enabling it to continue to receive default superannuation contribution from  january  executive leadershipedit the following individuals have been appointed to serve as chief executive of the commonwealth bank of australia or precursor titles order name title term start term end time in office reference  sir denison miller kcmg governor june   june   ♠ years  days   james kell june   october   ♠ years  days  sir ernest riddle october   february   ♠ years  days  sir harry sheehan cbe march   march   ♠ years  days  hugh armitage cmg july   december   ♠ years  days   dr h c coombs january   january   ♠ years  days   ernest richardson cbe managing director january   march   ♠ years  days   sir bede callaghan cbe may   august   ♠ years  days   sir ronald elliott august   august   ♠ years  days   v t christie ao august   march   ♠ years  days  d n sanders cb march   december   ♠ years  days chief executive officer january   june   ♠ year  days  david murray ao june   september   ♠ years  days  sir ralph norris knzm september   november   ♠ years  days  ian narev chief executive officer and managing director december   incumbent ♠ years  days international operationsedit the commonwealth banks international presence includes retail banks in new zealand asb bank and indonesia  of pt bank commonwealth banking investments in china  per cent in both qilu bank and 