er and pick n pay stores in south africa products and servicesedit the commonwealth bank is australias largest retail bank and offers customers a range of products and services including loans credit cards transaction and savings accounts it has the largest branch and atm networkcitation needed it also offers services to people planning to move to australiacitation needed subsidiariesedit australia comminsure commonwealth securities colonial first state bankwest new zealand asb sovereign asia pacific colonial national bank fiji pt bank commonwealth indonesia amtd group company limited hong kong galleryedit the state savings bank building in martin place used until  by the commonwealth bank commonwealth bank signage at the state savings bank building commonwealth bank signage at the banks headquarters building on the corner of pitt street and martin place see alsoedit australia portal business portal australian cricket academy banking in australia commonwealth bank series commonwealth bank trophy list of banks in australia list of banks in oceania list of companies of australia reserve bank of australia state bank of new south wales state bank of victoria referencesedit  commonwealth bank overview retrieved  august    a b c d e f g commonwealth bank of australia annual report  pdf  august  retrieved  august    commbankcomau  asx  list  market capitalisation accurate on  august  asx  australian securities exchange  august  retrieved  september    worlds largest banks by market capitalization  relbankscom    australia through time random house australia  p  isbn       commonwealth bank – history – a brief history of the commonwealth bank aboutcommbankcomau retrieved    httpunpanunorgintradocgroupspublicdocumentseropaunpanpdf  commonwealth bank of australia  commonwealth bank of australia to acquire bank west and st andrews retrieved    bank of western australia limited  bankwest and st andrews sold to commonwealth bank retrieved    aussie home loans and commonwealth ba